### Login
POST {{host}}/api/account/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vladimir2@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!"
}

### Generate IP report
POST {{host}}/api/reports/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ipAddress": "8.8.8.8"
}

### Get user's saved reports
GET {{host}}/api/reports
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get report by ID
GET {{host}}/api/reports/{{reportId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json